# Streaming SQL (ksqlDB) — streams/tables overview + query editor (global key: K)
Output vhs/gifs/ksql.gif
Source vhs/_config.tape

Hide
Type "./kafui --mock" Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Sleep 1500ms
# Open the ksqlDB overview
Type "K"
Sleep 3s
# Switch Tables / Streams tab
Tab
Sleep 2s
# Open the query editor
Type "e"
Sleep 2500ms
Escape
Sleep 1200ms

Hide
Ctrl+C
